data.title: The Law Society
data.text:
Where does this information come from? Most information on this page comes from the Solicitors Regulation Authority. However, some information may have been edited directly by the professional, firm or their representative. Find out more.

Are these your details? If you need to amend any information about you on Find a Solicitor or wish to give other feedback about the website, please call 020 7320 5757 (Monday to Friday from 09:00 to 17:00 charged at local call rates) or visit our contact us page.
